      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Normal Attack</span></p><p>Deals 1 <span style=\"color: #80FFD7\">Anemo DMG</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/08/26/35428890/1ce09211f025bf5470682189e0837732_2376752992452461019.png",
                "id": "talent16016",
                "key": "Word of Wind and Flower",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "anemo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "talent_imgs": [],
                "title": "Word of Wind and Flower"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>Deals 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">Anemo DMG</span>. Creates <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Skyladder</span>. This character gains <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Driftcloud Wave</span>.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Skyladder</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Combat Status</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">When you perform \"Switch Character\":</span> Spend 1 less Elemental Die.<br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage(s): 1</span> (Can stack. Max 2 stacks.)</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Driftcloud Wave</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Status</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">When you switch to the character to which this is attached:</span> Deal 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">Anemo DMG</span>.<br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage(s): 1 </span>(Can stack. Max 2 stacks.)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/08/26/35428890/79d2dc0ab0f7a0c36587bd40a2ba09b7_1954475474668961543.png",
                "id": "talent58943",
                "key": "White Clouds at Dawn",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "anemo"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "talent_imgs": [],
                "title": "White Clouds at Dawn"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Burst</span></p><p>Deals 1 <span style=\"color: #80FFD7\">Anemo </span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">DMG</span>. Heals all allied characters for 1 HP. Creates 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Starwicker </span>in your Hand.<br>(Characters with Starwicker equipped can use the Technique: <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Adeptal Assistance</span>)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/08/26/35428890/aff71fb8cfbf5594ea7f4fa18f456273_8067562957374377534.png",
                "id": "talent31806",
                "key": "Stars Gather at Dusk",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "anemo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "talent_imgs": [],
                "title": "Stars Gather at Dusk"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Equipment Card</span></p><p>Technique: Adeptal Assistance</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Usage(s): 2</span></p><p>(A character can only equip 1 technique at a time)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/08/26/35428890/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_2209581110093612384.png",
                "id": "talent6253",
                "key": "Starwicker",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/08/26/35428890/82c711b2a1c8eb2bb4bc97a0f6f3aeb3_3345908888532384353.png",
                "title": "Starwicker"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Technique</span></p><p>Heal the attached character for 2 HP. The next time this character uses a Normal Attack, it is considered as a <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Plunging Attack</span>, DMG +1. Also, after the Skill finalizes, deal <span style=\"color: #80FFD7\">Anemo DMG</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/08/26/35428890/0a55f17c8440010076312cb5bb6073be_8360915272742834577.png",
                "id": "talent45391",
                "key": "Adeptal Assistance",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "white"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Adeptal Assistance"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Reacts with Elements if they are already applied:<br>[<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">Anemo </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Cryo Swirl</span>: Deals 1 Cryo DMG to all opposing chracters except the target<br>[<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">Anemo </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Hydro Swirl:</span> Deals 1 Hydro DMG to all opposing characters except the target<br>[<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">Anemo </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Pyro Swirl</span>: Deals 1 Pyro DMG to all opposing characters except the target<br>[<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">Anemo </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Electro Swirl</span>: Deals 1 Electro DMG to all opposing characters except the target</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/08/26/35428890/c97292d96456bfe4abeca16bfce801e4_807881502283018932.png",
                "id": "talent62228",
                "key": "Anemo DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Anemo DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Usage(s)</span></strong></p><p>After this card's effect is triggered, 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage </span>of it will be consumed.</p><p>This card will be discarded immediately once it has 0 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usages </span>remaining.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Technique</span></strong></p><p>When the active character is equipped with a Technique card, they can use the corresponding Technique.<br>Using a Technique counts as a Combat Action. If the character is unable to use Skills due to conditions like Frozen, Petrification, or Stun, they are also unable to use the Technique.<br>Using a Technique is not considered as using a Skill. Therefore, it cannot trigger effects such as \"After using a skill\" or \"After the character triggers an Elemental Reaction.\" Damage dealt by using a Technique is not considered Damage dealt by the character.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Plunging Attack</span></strong></p><p>After a character is switched in to be the Active Character, should their next Combat Action within this Round be a Normal Attack, it will be considered a Plunging Attack for the instance.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/08/26/35428890/245c229cf6f7364c7c9a7aea3db1a1ad_8627056774229335894.png",
                "id": "talent32730",
                "key": "Detailed Rules",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Detailed Rules"
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
